As for the drivers, it is difficult to imagine what work will have to be done to overcome the age-old Russian conservatism.
In most cases, the driver will wait for hours for the inspector to register a minor accident, because it is safer that way.
And it is still unknown what will be easier - to defeat the scammers or convince the drivers of the reliability of the &quot;Europrotocol&quot;.
