Brussels and Washington noticed the balanced position of Minsk on the Ukrainian issue - and assessed it, Belarusian experts are sure.
How successful Lukashenka’s movement towards political diversification will turn out to be can be seen from how often Minsk will soon host meetings in the EU + CU format.
